<Verbatim PAsource="" >Police who searched him found he was wearing a pair of knickers and a lady's swimsuit.</Verbatim>


<Verbatim PAsource="" >Bearded Jeyakumar claimed they were to support his hernia, but when officers searched his home in Alperton, north west London, they found sacks full of </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >undies. </Rewrite>
